    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Boil a kettle</p><p>Add the<strong> huli huli chicken</strong> with any <strong>remaining huli huli sauce</strong> to a<strong> tin foil</strong>-lined tray and put under the grill for 5 min or until charred, caramelised and cooked through (no pink meat!) – this is your <strong>huli huli grilled chicken</strong></p><p>Return the pan to the heat with a small drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong>, add 1 <strong>pineapple ring </strong>per person and cook for 3-4 min, turning once until charred – this is your <strong>charred pineapple</strong></p>",
