    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, add your <strong>edamame beans</strong> to a colander and pour <strong>boiled water</strong> all over them to refresh them, then set aside to cool</p><p>Chop the<strong> remaining pineapple</strong> into bite-sized pieces</p>",
