    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine the <strong>refreshed edamame beans </strong>with your <strong>mayo</strong> and <strong>remaining sriracha</strong> in a bowl<strong> </strong>and mix everything together – these are your <strong>creamy sriracha edamame beans</strong></p>",
