    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>cooked</strong> <strong>sushi rice</strong> with the <strong>huli huli grilled chicken</strong>, <strong>chopped pineapple</strong>, <strong>creamy sriracha edamame beans</strong> and <strong>charred pineapple</strong> on top</p><p>Sprinkle your<strong> chilli flakes</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) over the chopped pineapple<strong> </strong>and top with the <strong>quick-pickled shallot</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
